ated as I try more authentic stuff on the menu. However, if your a white girl (or guy), who can handle spice, and loves Thai- GET HERE ASAP! Thank me later!", "fab as advertised", "lotus of siam has the best thai food in las vegas! been going there since it opened, and SAIPAN CHUTIMA and her family rocks the boat!!she has  been the top thai chef in las  vegas for years, and never fails to amaze with her delicious dishes. the wine list, especially the whites is superb.everything on the menu is top quality, and authentic tasting!!! thanks siapan and girls for a wonderful dining experience!!!!"]
