u can't go wrong. The servers work diligently and are extremely knowledgeable when it pertains to the entree recommendations based on the customer's preferences. The restaurant is modest in size, and possesses a really nice ambience. Make your reservations the day before you plan on dining, the don't do same day RSVPs."]
